For design stage:
1. Define workflow helper abstraction with hook-driven lifecycle
2. Specify dedupe key strategy (workflow-level, not just runtime-level)
3. Design idempotent cleanup with proper state machine
4. Document hook delivery assumptions with fallback strategies

